snippet.title: Cosmophobia - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Cosmophobia is an upcoming VR survival horror roguelike.
Wishlist it here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1256060/Cosmophobia/

Trapped in a dying spaceship filled with horrors, you must find your way back to the safety of Earth. Cosmophobia features a rich, immersive atmosphere that will make you forget about the world outside the headset.


More info: http://www.cosmophobiavr.com/
